    "The dataset encompasses 188,200 sentences, 491,711 entities, and 4,601,223 labels.",
    "The entities are classified into 8 broader categories and 66 more specific categories.",
    "The creators have established three benchmark tasks, involving one supervised task and two tasks with limited samples.",
    "• MSRA (Levow, 2006).",
    "The MSRA dataset is utilized in the NER task of the Third International Chinese LanguageProcessing Bakeoff."
